{{use British English|date=June 2015}} {{use mdy dates|date=June 2015}} {{Infobox award | name = World Travel Awards | subheader = | current_awards = | image = | alt = | caption = | description = | sponsor = | date = | location = Headquartered in [[London]], England | country = United Kingdom | presenter = | reward = | year = Established {{start date and age|1993|paren=yes}} | year2 = | website = {{URL|worldtravelawards.com}} | previous = | main = | next = }}
The '''World Travel Awards''' were founded in 1993. Annually, an international [[Juried (competition)|jury]] of hospitality experts and peers, mainly from the [[World Travel and Tourism Council]], decided on awards presented to [[hotel]]s and other [[hospitality]] companies.<ref>{{cite book |url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=DzvFWbOsiv0C&pg=PA289&dq=world+travel+awards&hl=en&sa=X&ei=VA3dVPHUGMOVyASlrIIY&ved=0CCkQ6AEwAg#v=onepage&q=world%20travel%20awards&f=false |title=Sustainability in the Hospitality Industry: Principles of Sustainable Operations |page=289 |author1=Sloan, Philip |author2=Legrand, Willy |author3=Chen, Joseph C. |author4=Chen, Joseph S. |publisher= [[Routledge]] |year=2012}}</ref>
Awards are given both on a world level and international region level in a wide range of categories.<ref>{{cite news |author = Staff | url=http://www.inquisitr.com/1830809/cayman-islands-earns-world-travel-award-anticipates-2015-win/ |publisher=Inquisitr |access-date= 24 June 2015 |date= 10 February 2015 |title=Cayman Islands Earns World Travel Award, Anticipates 2015 Win}}</ref> Categories include hotel, airline, travel agency, and car-hire company.
